The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Pargat demand
                                                                                                                                                                                                     Pargat demand
                      
	Jalandhar: Former hockey captain Pargat Singh on Wednesday demanded a CBI probe into the functioning of the IHF and said it should be restructured for the benefit of the sport. The Olympian said only a CBI inquiry would help in finding if the selection process was unbiased or otherwise. He also joined the chorus demanding the resignation of the K.P.S. Gill. (PTI)                                                                                                                          
